               <h1 property="name" id="wb-cont">Contact us about CRB</h1>
               <dl class="dl-horizontal brdr-0">
                  <dt>Online:</dt>
                  <dd><p>Use your CRA My Account to:</p>
                     <ul>
                        <li>apply for the Canada Recovery Benefit (CRB)</li>
                        <li>update your address and direct deposit information</li>
                     </ul>
                     <div class="mrgn-tp-md"> <a class="btn btn-call-to-action" href="https://www.canada.ca/en/revenue-agency/services/e-services/e-services-individuals/account-individuals.html">Sign in to CRA My Account</a>   <a href="/en/revenue-agency/services/e-services/e-services-individuals/account-individuals.html" class="mrgn-lft-md">Register</a> </div>
                  </dd>
                  <dt>By phone:</dt>
                  <dd>
                     <dl class="dl-horizontal brdr-0">
                        <p>Call the CRB general line for questions about:</p>
                        <ul>
                           <li>CRB eligibility requirements</li>
                           <li>how much you could get</li>
                           <li>how and when to apply</li>
                        </ul>
                        <dt><strong>Telephone number:</strong></dt>
                        <dd>
                           <a href="tel:18339662099" class="hidden-md hidden-lg nowrap"><span class="fas fa-phone fa-flip-horizontal"></span>1-833-966-2099<span class="wb-inv"> (opens up phone application)</span></a><strong class="hidden-xs hidden-sm nowrap"><span class="fas fa-phone fa-flip-horizontal"></span>1-833-966-2099</strong>
                        </dd>
                        <dt>Hours:</dt>
                        <dd>
                           <table class="table brdr-bttm">
                              <caption class="wb-inv">
                                 Dedicated CRB number hours
                              </caption>
                              <thead>
                                 <tr>
                                    <th class="wb-inv" scope="col">Date</th>
                                    <th class="wb-inv" scope="col">Hours</th>
                                 </tr>
                              </thead>
                              <tbody>
                                 <tr>
                                    <td>Monday to Friday</td>
                                    <td><strong>9&nbsp;am to 5&nbsp;pm</strong> (local time)</td>
                                 </tr>
                                 <tr>
                                    <td>Saturday</td>
                                    <td>Closed</td>
                                 </tr>
                                 <tr>
                                    <td>Sunday</td>
                                    <td>Closed</td>
                                 </tr>
                              </tbody>
                           </table>
                           <p>Closed on <a href="https://www.canada.ca/en/revenue-agency/services/tax/public-holidays.html">public holidays</a></p>
                        </dd>
                     </dl>
                     <p>Call the CRA general enquiries line for questions about your account information, including if you:</p>
                     <ul>
                        <li>have trouble applying for the CRB because you haven’t filed a tax return recently</li>
                        <li>want to make changes to your account (updates to address or direct deposit)</li>
                        <li>have trouble accessing CRA My Account </li>
                     </ul>
                                        
                     <dl class="dl-horizontal brdr-0">
                        <dt>Before you call:</dt>
                        <dd>
                           <p>To verify your identity, you'll need your:</p>
                           <ul>
                              <li>Social Insurance Number (SIN)</li>
                              <li>full name and date of birth</li>
                              <li>complete address</li>
                              <li>assessed return, notice of assessment or reassessment, other tax document, or be signed in to CRA My Account</li>
                           </ul>
                        </dd>
                        <dt><strong>Telephone number:</strong></dt>
                        <dd><a href="tel:18009598281" class="hidden-md hidden-lg nowrap"><span class="fas fa-phone fa-flip-horizontal"></span>1-800-959-8281<span class="wb-inv"> (opens up phone application)</span></a><strong class="hidden-xs hidden-sm nowrap"><span class="fas fa-phone fa-flip-horizontal"></span>1-800-959-8281</strong></dd>
                        <dt>Hours:</dt>
                        <dd>
                           <table class="table brdr-bttm">
                              <caption class="wb-inv">
                                 CRA’s General enquiries line hours
                              </caption>
                              <thead>
                                 <tr>
                                    <th class="wb-inv" scope="col">Date</th>
                                    <th class="wb-inv" scope="col">Hours</th>
                                 </tr>
                              </thead>
                              <tbody>
                                 <tr>
                                    <td>Monday to Friday</td>
                                    <td><strong>9&nbsp;am to 5&nbsp;pm</strong> (local time)</td>
                                 </tr>
                                 <tr>
                                    <td>Saturday</td>
                                    <td>Closed</td>
                                 </tr>
                                 <tr>
                                    <td>Sunday</td>
                                    <td>Closed</td>
                                 </tr>
                              </tbody>
                           </table>
                           <p>Closed on <a href="https://www.canada.ca/en/revenue-agency/services/tax/public-holidays.html">public holidays</a></p>
                        </dd>
                     </dl>
                  </dd>

               <dt>Report fraud:</dt>
               <dd>Call the <a href="https://antifraudcentre-centreantifraude.ca/report-signalez-eng.htm">Canadian Anti-fraud Centre</a> to report a scam or if you have concerns about a call or email you received about your CRB payment. 
                  <dl>
                     <dt>Telephone number:</dt>
                     <dd><strong><span class="fas fa-phone fa-flip-horizontal"></span>1-888-495-8501</strong></dd>
                  </dl>
               </dd>
            </dl>

